    "FullDescription": {
      "#cdata-section": "<p>#9 Ashland and #9X Ashland&nbsp;buses are temporarily rerouted in both directions, due to street blockage near&nbsp;Ashland/Congress.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Southbound</strong>&nbsp;buses will operate via Ashland, Jackson, Racine, Roosevelt then resume their normal route on Ashland.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Northbound</strong> buses will operate via Ashland. Roosevelt, Racine, Madison then resume their normal route on Ashland.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Allow extra travel time.</p>\r\n"
